text: Ilmurzino () is a rural locality (a village) in Starokamyshlinsky Selsoviet, Kushnarenkovsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 297 as of 2010. There are 9 streets. == Geography == It is located 39 km from Kushnarenkovo, 3 km from Starye Kamyshly. == References == Category:Rural localities in Kushnarenkovsky District
title: Ilmurzino
